text: National Highway 727BB, commonly referred to as NH 727BB is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 27. NH-727BB runs in the state of Uttar Pradesh in India. == Route == NH727BB connects Gorakhpur and Partawal in the state of Uttar Pradesh. == Junctions == : Terminal near Gorakhpur. : Terminal near Partawal. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 727BB on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Uttar Pradesh
